              "token": "b",
              "kind": "alpha_lower",
              "text": "Are culturally responsive and relevant to diverse learners;",
              "subsections": []
            },
            {
              "label": "(c)",
              "token": "c",
              "kind": "alpha_lower",
              "text": "Are based on long-term research derived from the science of reading and writing; and",
