          "token": "7",
          "kind": "numeric",
          "text": "(a) The department shall award grants under this section from moneys available in the School Stabilization Subaccount for Wildfire-impacted School Districts established under section 4 of this 2022 Act. (c) of this section. [2022 c.43 2] Sec. 3. Applicable school years.",
          "subsections": [
